      </div>
    
          <div class="card-inset-details__teaser-text">
        
            A new study finds that another youth perpetrates the behavior in 37 percent of cases of child sexual abuse, and almost all cases (97 percent) involve sexual grooming behaviors.
      
      </div>
    
